iet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Huong_dan_cach_Thiet_ke_to_roi_bang_Powerpoint\" title=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Nhung_thu_can_chuan_bi\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Cach_buoc_thiet_ke_to_roi_bang_Powerpoint\" title=\"C\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint\">C\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Buoc_1_Mo_giao_dien_Powerpoint_va_chon_loai_tuy_thich\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: M\u1edf giao di\u1ec7n Powerpoint v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i t\u00f9y th\u00edch.\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: M\u1edf giao di\u1ec7n Powerpoint v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i t\u00f9y th\u00edch.<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Buoc_2_Tuy_chinh_size\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh size\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh size<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Buoc_3_Chen_hinh_anh_vao_to_roi\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Ch\u00e8n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o t\u1edd r\u01a1i\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Ch\u00e8n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Buoc_4_Bien_tap_hinh_anh_noi_dung_lam_nhu_Powerpoint_thong_thuong\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Bi\u00ean t\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 Powerpoint th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Bi\u00ean t\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 Powerpoint th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-powerpoint.html\/#Buoc_5_Hoan_chinh_la_luu_to_roi_ve_may_tinh\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh l\u00e0 l\u01b0u t\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh.\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh l\u00e0 l\u01b0u t\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh.<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>C\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Microsoft Office c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/to-roi-quang-cao-du-lich.html\/\">m\u1eabu t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/a>. Tuy kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cth\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh\u201d nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/phan-mem-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/\">ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng<\/a> nh\u01b0 Photoshop, InDesign hay Illustrator nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd <strong>h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<\/strong> \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_Thiet_ke_to_roi_bang_Powerpoint\"><\/span><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>T\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p b\u1eb1ng PowerPoint c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. t\u1edd r\u01a1i gi\u00fap cho th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng cho c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng marketing, c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y tr\u00ean l\u1edbp n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_thu_can_chuan_bi\"><\/span>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>M\u00e1y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0i Office Powerpoint<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cho t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f3 kho t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-bang-word.html\/\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Word\u00a0<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_buoc_thiet_ke_to_roi_bang_Powerpoint\"><\/span>C\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_1_Mo_giao_dien_Powerpoint_va_chon_loai_tuy_thich\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: M\u1edf giao di\u1ec7n Powerpoint v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i t\u00f9y th\u00edch.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2952\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1edf-giao-di\u1ec7n-powerpoint-t\u00f9y-th\u00edch.png\" alt=\"h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i\" width=\"825\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1edf-giao-di\u1ec7n-powerpoint-t\u00f9y-th\u00edch.png 760w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1edf-giao-di\u1ec7n-powerpoint-t\u00f9y-th\u00edch-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_2_Tuy_chinh_size\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh size<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edd r\u01a1i: V\u00e0o Designe =&gt; custom slide size v\u00e0 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i. T\u00f9y v\u00e0o nhu c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc sao cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n OK.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<\/strong> b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh k\u00edch c\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a slide \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb. Ch\u00fang ta th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen nh\u00ecn slide d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng n\u1eb1m ngang, trong khi t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in theo chi\u1ec1u d\u1ecdc. t\u1edd r\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m theo b\u1ed1n lo\u1ea1i k\u00edch c\u1ee1, nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 8.5\u2033 x 11\u2033.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2953\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2953\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2953\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u00f9y-ch\u1ec9nh-size-b\u1ea1n-mong-mu\u1ed1n.png\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng power point\" width=\"825\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u00f9y-ch\u1ec9nh-size-b\u1ea1n-mong-mu\u1ed1n.png 734w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/t\u00f9y-ch\u1ec9nh-size-b\u1ea1n-mong-mu\u1ed1n-300x153.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2953\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh size b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_3_Chen_hinh_anh_vao_to_roi\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Ch\u00e8n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o t\u1edd r\u01a1i<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>L\u01b0u \u00fd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00e8n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_4_Bien_tap_hinh_anh_noi_dung_lam_nhu_Powerpoint_thong_thuong\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Bi\u00ean t\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 Powerpoint th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, ch\u1eef vi\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i trong PowerPoint. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu t\u1edd r\u01a1i tr\u00ean Microsoft Office.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c m\u1eabu template PowerPoint c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng infographic template n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lu\u00f4n, \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c khung s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda, thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n, c\u00e1c bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo \u00fd m\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2954\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/bi\u00ean-t\u1eadp-h\u00ecnh-\u1ea3nh-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-v\u1eafn-t\u1eaft.png\" alt=\"h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn l\u00e0m poster qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \" width=\"825\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/bi\u00ean-t\u1eadp-h\u00ecnh-\u1ea3nh-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-v\u1eafn-t\u1eaft.png 770w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/bi\u00ean-t\u1eadp-h\u00ecnh-\u1ea3nh-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-v\u1eafn-t\u1eaft-300x162.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/bi\u00ean-t\u1eadp-h\u00ecnh-\u1ea3nh-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-v\u1eafn-t\u1eaft-768x414.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_5_Hoan_chinh_la_luu_to_roi_ve_may_tinh\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh l\u00e0 l\u01b0u t\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u00e0o file =&gt; save as \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u01b0u.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2955\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2955\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2955\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/save-as-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i.png\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng power point\" width=\"825\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/save-as-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i.png 769w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/save-as-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-300x160.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/save-as-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-768x408.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2955\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Save as t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Khi ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u01b0u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean file \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng l\u01b0u file \u1ea3nh l\u00e0 \u0111u\u00f4i jpg.<\/p>\n<p>M\u00e1y t\u00ednh s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n l\u01b0u to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh trong slide hay ch\u1ec9 l\u01b0u 1 \u1ea3nh. T\u00f9y v\u00e0o nhu c\u1ea7u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n<p>Sau khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn xong th\u00ec ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint nh\u01b0 n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2956\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2956\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2956\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ea3n-ph\u1ea3m-ho\u00e0n-thi\u1ec7n.png\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf poster qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\" width=\"825\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ea3n-ph\u1ea3m-ho\u00e0n-thi\u1ec7n.png 767w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ea3n-ph\u1ea3m-ho\u00e0n-thi\u1ec7n-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2956\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><em>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0\u00a0<strong>h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint<\/strong>\u00a0m\u00e0 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 r\u00f5 n\u00e9t c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. H\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/\"><strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0ngay nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Microsoft Office c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1eabu t\u1edd r\u01a1i. Tuy kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cth\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh\u201d nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Photoshop, InDesign hay Illustrator nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2957,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[51,56],"tags":[226,230,105,229],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng Powerpoint - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p marketing t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0ng \u